headline: WEST ELM LAUNCHES COLLABORATION WITH POPULAR INTERIOR DESIGN DUO, PIERCE & WARD
summary: BROOKLYN, NY, March 31, 2025--Global design company, West Elm, a portfolio brand of Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM), the world’s largest digital-first, design-led and sustainable home retailer, announced today a new collaboration with renowned interior design duo, Pierce & Ward. Co-founders Louisa Pierce and Emily Ward have partnered with the West Elm team to design a new collection that reflects the popular design duo’s distinctive, award-winning aesthetic that blends vintage charm and modern
